  <brief_title>EZN-2279 in Patients With ADA-SCID</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study of EZN-2279 (Polyethylene Glycol Recombinant Adenosine Deaminase [PEG-rADA]) Administered as a Weekly Intramuscular Injection in Patients With Adenosine Deaminase (ADA)-Deficient Combined Immunodeficiency</official_title>
