  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety, efficacy, and pharmacokinetics of
      EZN-2279 in patients with ADA-deficient combined immunodeficiency currently being treated
      with Adagen.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
